		<p class="tag-list">Tags: <a href="http://www.pikachews.com/tag/eggs/" rel="tag">eggs</a>, <a href="http://www.pikachews.com/tag/how-to/" rel="tag">how-to</a>, <a href="http://www.pikachews.com/tag/soft-boiled/" rel="tag">soft boiled</a></p>
